# Deployment (Vercel)

- This project is **hosted on Vercel** (connected to the Git repo).
- **Deploy:** push to the branch Vercel watches (usually `main`) — Vercel builds and publishes automatically.
- **Static output:** root `index.html`, `app.js`, `styles.css`, assets — no separate build step required unless the user adds one.
- If deploy advice is needed, assume **Vercel dashboard + Git integration**, not FTP/cPanel unless stated otherwise.
